Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂嗎  明天我還是去那裏吧  一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂  是指姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是姐姐的男朋友  明天約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.21,0:00:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的話  現在在洗澡  為明天做準備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想聊聊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  一邊玩去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  是待機畫面的那個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫伊藤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太好了  剛才嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  妹妹她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  叫「心」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  雖是姐妹卻是不同的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  很多人和我這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  就叫你妹妹「小心」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「桂」也是這樣  罕見的名字真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  上次  妹妹她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心接電話的那事嗎  我沒有在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子想跟伊藤同學見一面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說  可以去桂的家裏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠  你太為難人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:04:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我倒是沒什麼關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 世界  桂都說可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同學  縱容他可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙本來就愣頭愣腦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不情願的時候就要斷然拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  世界小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請你不要打斷好不容易取得進展的對話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  看招  看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好疼  世界  很疼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話少說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂  午休時去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不在  這些東西就被推到我頭上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你可是校園祭實行委員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會給我們增加很多負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是  去見男朋友了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是男的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪一下就不見人影了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說嘛  桂的男朋友是個怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問了也沒用吧  那種傢伙的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思  比起實行委員的工作  男朋友更重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話就好好幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  那份東西  之後要做好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起校園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙女已經決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過完全沒當回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就做好失敗的準備  試試而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真順利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰上什麼事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去沒什麼精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下站是原巳濱  原巳濱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:06:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是發生了什麼  不要客氣跟我說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是戀人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們  是戀人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原巳濱  原巳濱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門即將關閉  請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那   我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}你的男朋友和4班的\N那個溫順的女孩\N好像有什麼情形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  不是男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已發送
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又讓桂同學為難了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要裝傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有人的地方下手真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是抱了下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要分場合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是戀人  有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  女孩子可是既會害羞又講氣氛的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是隨時隨地怎麼樣都行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是戀人也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「哎」什麼  總是把自己的意識強加於別人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同學又要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  這種事情要考慮對方的心情  若無其事地做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩也要那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是跨越了那段不明白對方心情的令人焦急的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦心意相通的時候才會更加地覺得開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才叫做戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.25,0:09:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  今天的事情可要好好道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  明天要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原巳濱  原巳濱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發車  關門請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  桂…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:52.97,STAFF,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\pos(275,96)\bord1\fs16\fscy90\fscx110}SumiSora&CASO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  誠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對桂同學道歉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電車上沒碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算現在也必須去4班…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因為誠太不著急了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  早上開始就打情罵俏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  世界也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一起來的話只會產生反效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是戀人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  你說過今天的午飯要和光她們一起吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  偶爾也要去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就是這樣了  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在陰笑什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多開始討論學園祭的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了乙女戀愛的成功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙女真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那樣的傢伙交往的話絕對會不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說是誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  難道最近世界不合群的原因是伊藤嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  真的和誠沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫「誠」了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人感覺很親密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為是同桌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那傢伙是瞄準換座位這機會出手的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是那樣的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭也快到了  不管哪裏都是這類話題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說一起逛學園祭的話就是公認情侶了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以性急的人事先開始準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備還順利嗎？班長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多我們班也要決定要舉辦的活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班要做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是要多數決定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是簡單點的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按傳統的話就是咖啡店  鬼屋什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪個看起來都很費事就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂還在生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我昨天在電車上…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  上次談到的小心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就有空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  有點太突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是星期天你有空的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我一定要來拜訪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂的家離車站有多遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  步行的話  大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待啊  穿什麼去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆買件新的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那到這裏  來真是難得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有的事  正好閒著沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是來看看你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會有想這樣做的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有1小時我就下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您要點些什麼呢  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季節限定  大份抹茶糯米團蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲料要冰咖啡  不加糖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦  讓你等那麼久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你找我到底有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你以為我們做了多少年朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我問了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的沒和伊藤交往嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  連剎那都誤會了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的和誠之間什麼事都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  被邀請了不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？ 那天要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一個人邊寂寞地工作邊祈禱你們幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  是真人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧  心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照了  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小心真是不客氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學要檸檬還是牛奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  心太調皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  謝謝你  桂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個那個  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼哥哥會叫姐姐「桂」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  心問了奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我沒想到桂會在意這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱呼真的有那麼重要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然重要了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…桂？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起  請別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…  言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠…君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於有戀人的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上電車就要進站了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請退到線後等待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.65,0:21:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能閉上一會兒眼睛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.47,0:22:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車就要開動了
